This paper deals with privacy-preserving social graph publication, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves optimisation problems and heuristics, which are topics related to computational intelligence (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the structure of social networks, which is a topic related to social and information networks (cs.SD). Additionally, the paper involves graph theory and algorithms, which are topics related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB).
